<item>
            <title>[SPARK-1348] Spark UI&apos;s do not bind to localhost interface anymore</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-1348</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running the shell or standalone master, it no longer binds to localhost. I think this may have been caused by the security patch. We should figure out what caused it and revert to the old behavior. Maybe we want to always bind to `localhost` or just to bind to all interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12704517">SPARK-1348</key>
            <summary>Spark UI&apos;s do not bind to localhost interface anymore</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
